  <discussion>Variety glaberrimum is localized and known with certainty from only five locations in the Warner Mountains of Lake County, Oregon, and Modoc County, California. A collection supposedly gathered somewhere in Klamath County, Oregon (Austin &amp; Bruce 1758, DS) in 1897 is discounted. This expression of the species is worthy of introduction into cultivation.</discussion>
